						"description": "Download a file by its ID. The file is streamed directly to the client with proper headers:\n- Content-Disposition: attachment\n- Content-Type: original file type\n- Content-Length: file size\n- X-File-Checksum: SHA-256 hash\n\nThe system automatically:\n- Verifies user authorization\n- Decrypts storage path\n- Resolves storage node\n- Streams file content"
